{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage every function of the rig, from resource extraction and equipment maintenance to ensuring the crew's safety. Your decisions have real consequences \u2013 will you handle a malfunction on your own, or call for help?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/Platform_move.gif?t=1728559854\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Each day brings new challenges: changing weather conditions, equipment failures, and unexpected crises. With a first-person perspective, you\u2019ll experience every aspect of life on the rig firsthand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/mantain.png?t=1728559854\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/Repair.gif?t=1728559854\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expand your platform, upgrade equipment, and take care of your crew to ensure smooth operations in the harsh conditions of the open sea. The day-night cycle and realistically simulated weather conditions mean that every decision matters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/manage.png?t=1728559854\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/Rentgen.gif?t=1728559854\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from a wide range of tools and techniques to tackle problems \u2013 from minor repairs to complex rescue operations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251540/extras/extract.png?t=1728559854\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"http